title: Cant find SEA server
body: I moved to Indonesia and i had a account in Eu West . When i play on this server my ping is 300. When i play in ocania i need 10 minutes to find a normal game . So what Server should i play when

replies.body: The SEA servers are hosted by Garena. They'll be able to help you along getting an account created there if you want by shooting them a ticket here -> http://intl.garena.com/support/
